\begin{gathered} 2 ( A + \lambda I ) x + 2 b = 0 \\ x^H x = c \end{gathered}
x=-(A+\lambda I)^{-1}b, \quad x^Hx = \| (A+\lambda I)^{-1} b \|_2^2
